WEBVTT

00:01:58.031 --> 00:02:00.862
another important
public service job, teaching,

00:02:00.886 --> 00:02:02.887
average age of teachers is 42.

00:02:03.950 --> 00:02:06.283
Our farmers are pretty old
in this country.

00:02:06.307 --> 00:02:08.268
And unfortunately,

00:02:08.292 --> 00:02:11.862
when they retire, if they retire,

00:02:11.886 --> 00:02:13.768
we're not really replacing them.

00:02:13.792 --> 00:02:16.053
Of all the farmers
that we added in this country

00:02:16.077 --> 00:02:18.576
between 2008 and 2012,

00:02:18.600 --> 00:02:20.695
across the entire United States --

00:02:20.719 --> 00:02:22.613
see if you can catch this difference --

00:02:22.637 --> 00:02:25.369
we added 2,000 under the age of 30.

00:02:25.393 --> 00:02:27.402
I'm one of those.

00:02:27.426 --> 00:02:30.315
I'll be around to autograph
some photos later, if you'd like.